Interface ExecutorFragmentContext

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable, ExchangeFragmentContext, FragmentContext, RootFragmentContext, UdfUtilities
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FragmentContextImpl, PhysicalOpUnitTestBase.MockExecutorFragmentContext

    public interface ExecutorFragmentContext
extends RootFragmentContext
    This interface represents the context that is used by a Drillbit in classes like the FragmentExecutor.
